import { Grid, TextField } from '@material-ui/core'
import React,{useState} from 'react'

export default function DCandidateForm(props) {
  return (
    <form autoComplete='off' noValidate>
      <Grid container>
        <Grid item xs={6}>
          <TextField
               name="fullName"
               variant='outlined'
               label='Full Name'></TextField>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </form>
  )
}
